{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=7b561a3067adb94fae4fc979d43e5b41&src=http%3A%2F%2Fa.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fd000baa1cd11728b677e270ec0fcc3cec3fd2c4e.jpg","summary":"内蒙古能源职业学院创建于1997年，是经内蒙古自治区政府批准、国家教育部备案，具有独立颁发国家高等教育学历证书资格，纳入国家计划内招生的一所民办全日制以能源为主的综合性普通高校。学院下设能源动力系、电力工程系、煤油化工系、建筑工程系、交通运输系、五年制大专部、建筑职业技术学校(中专)及高等继续教育学院，开设以城市热能、石油煤炭、光伏风电、燃气化工、电力管理等紧缺“订单”专业20余个特色、品牌专业，在校生千余人来自全国十余个省、市、自治区。学院位于呼和浩特市新城区，占地面积150余亩，校舍建筑总面积5万多平方米，拥有校园网络、多媒体演示、电子阅览等先进教学设备。办学以来，累计向社会输送毕业生数以万名，主要工作在区内外电力和新能源行业。","tags":["理工类","专科","民办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1997","所在地区":"内蒙古呼和浩特市新城区呼哈路6公里处","院校隶属":"内蒙古自治区教育厅"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=fde61e60b53843aa284c016a4cbb9ae1&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3653980738%2C722104315%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=1a5bd87d70a719173768c0cdd4462270&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3652304525%2C749184157%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=649025cd564e22ae97ea05b5ac651f57&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3485505225%2C4080306881%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=41bc3a04c3c40487b9bc614b122f5b0b&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2917673346%2C2880540937%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534493476&di=c3bc602505413ad17cb0694a3db39de4&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3537145349%2C794872763%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT